  "lineage": {
    "statement": "Sentinel-2 MSI data is systematically processed to Level-2A using the Sen2Cor atmospheric correction processor. The processing includes radiometric calibration, geometric correction, cloud and cloud shadow detection, and atmospheric correction to derive bottom-of-atmosphere reflectance.",
